  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区进入医院，再到出院的完整路径，但重点要突出\"出院受阻\"这个系统性问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "Inpatient",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，是想表现患者流转中的瓶颈。起点是社区吗？患者一般怎么进入医院系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，社区是起点。患者可以通过两条路径：一是先看GP，也就是全科医生；二是直接急诊就诊。这两条路径最终都汇聚到急诊。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，社区分出两条线到GP和ED_Arrival，然后GP也指向ED_Arrival。接下来急诊之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "急诊到达之后是急诊评估和治疗，英文我们叫ED_Treat。这是关键节点，用红色系标注会比较醒目。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ED_Treat节点，用了state样式，浅红底色配深红边框。然后这个节点指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat之后是\"决定是否收治\"，Admission这个决策点。然后才是正式的住院，Inpatient。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程是ED_Treat → Admission → Inpatient。Inpatient也要用state样式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Admission",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Inpatient和ED_Treat一样，都是核心状态节点。住院之后，患者会到达一个关键阶段——\"准备出院\"，Ready。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Inpatient和Ready都加上了。现在到重点部分了，您说的\"出院受阻\"具体指什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Ready节点会分出两个主要的阻塞点。一个是老年护理床位不足，Block_Aged；另一个是NDIS支持或住宿安排延迟，Block_NDIS。这两个都是容量约束类的风险。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个阻塞点需要特殊视觉区分吗？听起来像是负面因素。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用橙色虚线框，risk样式。而且这两个不是终点，它们会形成反馈循环——患者卡在这两个环节，实际上还是占用着Inpatient床位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "反馈循环我理解了，就是Block_Aged和Block_NDIS虚线连回Inpatient？需要标注反馈机制的文字吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Block_Aged那条标注\"occupancy feedback loop\"，表示床位占用的反馈。另外，还有一个更直接的反馈：高住院率会反过来限制急诊流转，Inpatient虚线连回ED_Treat，标注\"high occupancy limits flow\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两条虚线反馈都加上了，虚线样式区分于主流程。我检查一下整体结构——Community、GP、ED_Arrival、ED_Treat、Admission、Inpatient、Ready，然后分出Block_Aged和Block_NDIS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "GP那个节点，我们内部叫CTH pathway，用蓝色系比较好，和红色的state节点区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "GP节点已调整为cth样式，浅蓝底色。其他中性节点像Community、ED_Arrival、Admission、Ready用灰色neutral样式可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Admission",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样视觉层次很清晰：蓝色是社区医疗路径，红色是院内状态，橙色虚线是风险阻塞，灰色是过渡节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Community"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Block_NDIS的标注需要调整吗？现在写的是\"NDIS supports / accommodation<br(delay / mismatch)\"，会不会太长？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "长度可以，换行显示没问题。不过Block_Aged的\"Aged care placement\"前面最好加上\"block\"的语义，让读者一眼看出这是阻塞点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已修正，Block_Aged显示为\"Aged care placement<br(capacity constraint)\"，括号里注明容量约束。整体检查一遍：主流程从左到右，反馈循环用虚线回指，颜色区分功能类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ED_Arrival到ED_Treat的箭头方向确认一下，是单向的对吧？患者不会从治疗状态回到刚到达的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，ED_Arrival → ED_Treat是单向实线箭头。只有那两条标注了feedback和occupancy的是虚线双向反馈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认一下字体用Inter，整体风格简洁专业。这个图的核心信息是：出院准备完成不等于真正出院，两个阻塞点会造成床位占用反馈，最终反噬急诊收治能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部设置完成，字体Inter 14px，主题色已统一。图已经可以展示access block mechanism的完整逻辑了。",
